# Cấu hình non-secret cho Cloud Functions theo project Firebase — bắt buộc commit
# (theo doc: https://firebase.google.com/docs/functions/config-env).
# Secrets thực sự đi qua Secret Manager (`firebase functions:secrets:set`).
!functions/.env.*

